{"lemma":"شَقَّةُ","slug":"شَقَّةُ","root":"ش.ق.ق","root_slug":"ش-ق-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ق-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"شَقَّةُ","root":"شقق","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":14},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n22690","n22701","n22702"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8E%D9%82%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"apartment, flat (domicile occupying part of a building)","examples":[{"text":"دَخَلَتْ سُلُطَاتُ ٱلْعَاصِمَةِ ٱلْاِقْتِصَادِيَّةِ مَرْحَلَةَ ٱلسُّرْعَةِ ٱلْقُصْوَى مِنْ أَجْلِ تَنْزِيلِ مَشْرُوعِ 62 أَلْفَ شُقَّةٍ سَكَنِيَّةٍ سَيَسْتَفِيدُ مِنْهَا قَاطِنُو دُورِ ٱلصَّفِيحِ بِٱلدَّارِ ٱلْبَيْضَاءِ وَٱلْمَنَاطِقِ ٱلْمُجَاوِرَةِ."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"compartment"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"half, moiety"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"piece"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"piece of land, tract, zone"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"splinter"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"trouble, difficulty"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"rift, split"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"destination (of a journey)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"distance"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"oblong piece of cloth (for wrapping a woman's body)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"trouble, difficulty"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"destination (of a journey)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"distance"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʃaq.qa/","/ʃiq.qa/","/ʃuq.qa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n22690","headword_ar":"شَقَّهُ","root":"$q","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Msb,)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1576},{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~N","text_ar":"شَقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut it"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"divided it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lengthwise;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qd","text_ar":"قد"},{"kind":"text","text":";) [i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he clave it, split it, rived"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rifted it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slit it; so as to separate it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he clave, split, rived"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rifted, slit, rent, ripped, tore, broke,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"burst, it asunder;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without separating it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he cracked, chapped, incided"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"incised, gashed, slashed, furrowed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trenched, it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clave, split,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut, it open;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SadaEahu","text_ar":"صَدَعَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) or [more explicitly]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~aq~u","text_ar":"الشَّقُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~adoEu AlbaAy^inu","text_ar":"الصَّدْعُ البَايِنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the cleaving"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that separates"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayoru AlbaAy^ini","text_ar":"غَيْرُ البَايِنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that which does not separate"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~adoEu","text_ar":"الصَّدْعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the cleaving,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a general sense:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) and in like manner, [but with an intensive signification, or implying frequency or repetition of the action, or its application to several objects, generally meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he clave it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in pieces,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in several places,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$q~qhu","text_ar":"شقّقهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$q~q AlHaTaba","text_ar":"شقّق الحَطَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wagayorahu","text_ar":"وَغَيْرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~ahu","text_ar":"شَقَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[but properly meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He clave in pieces the firewood &c."},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K. [In the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a AlHaTaba","text_ar":"شَقَّ الحَطَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$q~q","text_ar":"شقّق"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHTb","text_ar":"الحطب"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b2-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a raA^osahu","text_ar":"شَقَّ رَاْسَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"generally means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He clave his head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his pericranium:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and sometimes, as in an instance in the K voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aqaA^a","text_ar":"شَقَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he divided the hair of his head."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a AlEaSaA","text_ar":"شَقَّ العَصَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He split the staff"},{"kind":"text","text":"] means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he separated himself from the community;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA;) and particularly, that of the Muslims: because the staff is not thus called but when it is whole, not when it is split: accord. to Lth,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ya$uq~u EaSaA Almusolimiyna","text_ar":"يَشُقُّ عَصَا المُسْلِمِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yu$aAq~uhumo","text_ar":"يُشَاقُّهُمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify alike: but they differ in meaning, as will be shown hereafter. (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a EaSaA Almusolimiyna","text_ar":"شَقَّ عَصَا المُسْلِمِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", K, TA,) said of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaArijiY~","text_ar":"خَارِجِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. heretic or schismatic], also means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He effected disunion and dissension in the body of the Muslims."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And one says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a EaSaA AlT~aAEapi","text_ar":"شَقَّ عَصَا الطَّاعَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He broke the compact of allegiance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obedience; became a rebel"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA waAl~a*iY $aq~a Alr~ijaAla liloxayoli waAljibaAla lils~ayoli","text_ar":"لَا وَالَّذِى شَقَّ الرِّجَالَ لِلْخَيْلِ وَالجِبَالَ لِلسَّيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"No, by Him who clave men for"},{"kind":"text","text":"the riding upon"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"horses, and the mountains for"},{"kind":"text","text":"the flowing of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the torrent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is a saying mentioned by IAar, but not expl. by him. (M. [It is there added,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waEinodiY A^an~ahu jaEala Alr~ijaAla waAljibaAla jumolapF","text_ar":"وَعِنْدِى اَنَّهُ جَعَلَ الرِّجَالَ وَالجِبَالَ جُمْلَةً"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAHidapF vum~a xaraqahumaA fajaEala Alr~ijaAla lih`*ihi waAljibaAla lih`*aA","text_ar":"وَاحِدَةً ثُمَّ خَرَقَهُمَا فَجَعَلَ الرِّجَالَ لِهٰذِهِ وَالجِبَالَ لِهٰذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":": an expression of opinion which is, to me, by no means clear, though reconcilable with my rendering.]) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaAlu bayonanaA $aq~a AlA^abolamapi","text_ar":"المَالُ بَيْنَنَا شَقَّ الاَبْلَمَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^ubolumapi","text_ar":"الاُبْلُمَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The property is"},{"kind":"text","text":"divided"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between us as in the dividing of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ablmp","text_ar":"ابلمة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the cattle are"},{"kind":"text","text":"divided &c.;] means we are equal in respect of the property, or cattle: for the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ablmp","text_ar":"ابلمة"},{"kind":"text","text":"means the [kind of leaf called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuwSap","text_ar":"خُوصَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", which, when it is split lengthwise, splits in halves: (M:) or, accord. to Aboo-Ziyád, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ablmp","text_ar":"ابلمة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a herb, or leguminous plant, ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baqolapN","text_ar":"بَقْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) to which there come forth pods, like [those of] the bean; and when you split them lengthwise, they split in halves, equally, from the first part to the last thereof:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a","text_ar":"شَقَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is in the accus. case as an inf. n.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$oquwqN","text_ar":"مَشْقُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being understood. (Har p. 639.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iq~N","text_ar":"شِقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a","text_ar":"شَقَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uquwqN","text_ar":"شُقُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) said of the canine tooth of a camel, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clave the gum and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"came forth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K, TA:) [said to be] a dial. var. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aqaA^a","text_ar":"شَقَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) and said of the canine tooth of a child, (M, TA,) in like manner, (TA,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it made its first appearance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) and said also of a plant, [as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it came forth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on the ground's first cleaving open from it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.) ―         -b7-  Also, aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~N","text_ar":"شَقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of the dawn, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It rose;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though it clave the place of its rising and came forth therefrom. (TA.) ―         -b8-  Also, aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~N","text_ar":"شَقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of lightning, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clave the clouds, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extended high, into the midst of the sky, without going to the right and left:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) so says A'Obeyd: (TA: [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aqiyqN","text_ar":"شَقِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"An$q~","text_ar":"انشقّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t$q~q","text_ar":"تشقّق","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of lightning, signify"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AinoEaq~a","text_ar":"اِنْعَقَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[probably meaning the same; (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaqiyqapN","text_ar":"عَقِيقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";) or, as expl. in the S and also in the O, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eq","text_ar":"عق"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, in a state of commotion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taDar~aba","text_ar":"تَضَرَّبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the clouds"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (M, TA:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t$q~q","text_ar":"تشقّق","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of lightning means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it spread wide and long."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a Als~abiyla","text_ar":"شَقَّ السَّبِيلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ebr","text_ar":"عبر"},{"kind":"text","text":") (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He passed along the way;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though he cut it, or furrowed it. (TK in that art.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a Aln~ahora","text_ar":"شَقَّ النَّهْرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He crossed the river by swimming."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qTE","text_ar":"قطع"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a AlmaA='a","text_ar":"شَقَّ المَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He opened a way, passage, vent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"channel, for the water to flow forth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bajasahu","text_ar":"بَجَسَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bjs","text_ar":"بجس"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b11-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a A^amorahu","text_ar":"شَقَّ اَمْرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~N","text_ar":"شَقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, discomposed, deranged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disordered, so that it became incongruous,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inconsistent, his affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state of affairs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.) [A phrase similar to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a AlEaSaA","text_ar":"شَقَّ العَصَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", mentioned above. And so, app., what next follows.] ―         -b12-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a AlkalaAma","text_ar":"شَقَّ الكَلَامَ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qad~ahu","text_ar":"قَدَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[also expl. as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaTaEahu","text_ar":"قَطَعَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which generally means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut short,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"broke off, the speech;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ceased from speaking;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but sometimes, and perhaps in this case,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he articulated speech,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the speech:"},{"kind":"text","text":"compare a signification of 2.]. (M and L in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qd","text_ar":"قد"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b13-  See also 8. ―         -b14-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a baSaru Almay~iti","text_ar":"شَقَّ بَصَرُ المَيِّتِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$axaSa","text_ar":"شَخَصَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The eye,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eyes, of the dying man became fixedly open;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his eyelids became raised upwards, and he looked intently, and became disquieted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disturbed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (M, TA:) and (TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the dying man looked at a thing, his sight not recoiling to him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA:) said of him to whom death is present: (S, TA:) or [simply]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the eyes of the dying man became open:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) one should not say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a Almay~itu baSarahu","text_ar":"شَقَّ المَيِّتُ بَصَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, M, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uq~a","text_ar":"شُقَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$","text_ar":"ش"},{"kind":"text","text":", is not approved. (IAth, TA.) ―         -b15-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a Ealayohi","text_ar":"شَقَّ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K, in the S"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY~a","text_ar":"عَلَىَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and in the Msb"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalayonaA","text_ar":"عَلَيْنَا"},{"kind":"text","text":",) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~N","text_ar":"شَقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$aq~apN","text_ar":"مَشَقَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) [or the latter is a simple subst., as seems to be indicated in the M and Msb,] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing, S, or an affair, or event, M, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affected him severely; had a severe effect upon him; distressed, afflicted, troubled, molested, inconvenienced, fatigued,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wearied, him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was difficult, hard, distressing, grievous,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"severe, to him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"onerous, burdensome, oppressive,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"troublesome, to him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~a Ealayohi","text_ar":"شَقَّ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [inf. n., app.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~N","text_ar":"شَقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"only,] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He caused him to fall into a difficult, hard, distressing, grievous,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"severe, case:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"imposed upon him that which was onerous, burdensome, oppressive,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"troublesome."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aq~ati Als~aforapu","text_ar":"شَقَّتِ السَّفْرَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The journey was"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficult, hard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"far-extending."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uq~a","text_ar":"شُقَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of the solid hoof, and of the pastern of a horse or the like,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, affected with the disease termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uqaAq","text_ar":"شُقَاق"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"occasioning cracks."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n22701","headword_ar":"شُقَّةٌ","root":"$q","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"primarily signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"half of a garment"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consisting of two oblong pieces sewed together, side by side"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: then it was applied to ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a garment as it is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when complete:"},{"kind":"text","text":"in both of these senses it is used in the present day]: (Er-Rághib, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiToEapN","text_ar":"قِطْعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a garment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uq~ap","text_ar":"شُقَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"viyaAb","text_ar":"ثِيَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[thus, and thus only, in the S, meaning of garments and of cloths, for it is of both,] is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an oblong piece;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabiybapN musotaTiylapN","text_ar":"سَبِيبَةٌ مُسْتَطِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) [it is often applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an oblong piece of cloth of those pieces of which a tent is composed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uqaqN","text_ar":"شُقَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iqaAqN","text_ar":"شِقَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, Mgh, TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN yabiyEu $iqaAqa Alkat~aAni","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ يَبِيعُ شِقَاقَ الكَتَّانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one sells pieces,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"oblong pieces,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of linen"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mazaAdap","text_ar":"مَزَادَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (B, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bSr","text_ar":"بصر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tract,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of Hell; likewise pronounced ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iq~apN","text_ar":"شِقَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ham p. 816.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A far journey;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iq~apN","text_ar":"شِقَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) sometimes thus pronounced with kesr: (S:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a far, long journey: a far-extending space:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a road difficult to him who travels it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or [simply]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a journey:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vnyA","text_ar":"ثنيا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[so in my copy of the Msb, app. a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaniy~ap","text_ar":"ثَنِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mountain-road,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uqaqN","text_ar":"شُقَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A part, region, quarter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tract,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Arafeh, Er-Rághib, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"towards which one draws near,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Arafeh, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"towards which the traveller directs himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uk~apN","text_ar":"شُكَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the reaching of which one is overtaken by difficulty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distress;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA;) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iq~apN","text_ar":"شِقَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same. (K.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Distance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iq~apN","text_ar":"شِقَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b7-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iq~N","text_ar":"شِقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence but one."}],"source_refs":["Mgh","M","K","S","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n22702","headword_ar":"شِقَّةٌ","root":"$q","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A splinter"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that splits off,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Mgh, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"split off,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA,) of a plank, (S, M, K, TA,) or of wood, (TA,) or of a piece of wood, (S, Mgh,) or other thing: (M, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece split,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"divided, lengthwise,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a staff, or stick, and of a garment, or piece of cloth, &c.: (IDrd, O, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece split"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) from anything;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as the half:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iqaqN","text_ar":"شِقَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, TA.) One says of him who is angry,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiHotad~a faTaArato minohu $iq~apN fiY AlA^aroDi wa$iq~apN fiY Als~amaA='i","text_ar":"اِحْتَدَّ فَطَارَتْ مِنْهُ شِقَّةٌ فِى الاَرْضِ وَشِقَّةٌ فِى السَّمَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became excited by sharpness of temper,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"angriness, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"he was as though"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a bit flew from him upon the ground, and a bit into the sky"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, * M, TA: in the S,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fY AlArD","text_ar":"فى الارض"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. is omitted.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iq~N","text_ar":"شِقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first three sentences. ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uq~apN","text_ar":"شُقَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places. ―         -b3-  And see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iq~N","text_ar":"شِقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", again, last sentence but one."}],"source_refs":["S","K","M","Mgh","TA","IDrd","O"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}